{"tid":1085194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李城下季正式向BIG6下戰書","createTime":"2019-03-31T04:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T08:15:03.000Z","uid":92376,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8dbdf0a59fab6e6c08e6fc374a82ad4f97751e","tid":1085194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"李斯特城堅稱他們要留住隊內的關鍵球員，並強調英超Big6不用想著試圖挖角了。<br />\n<br />\n麥迪臣本賽季在英超中表現搶眼，有消息稱熱刺在關注他。不過，李斯特城老闆艾耶禾特和羅渣士堅稱，如果有豪門球隊想要簽下這些和球隊簽署了長約的球員，球會不會向求購者退縮。<br />\n<br />\n鏡報稱，艾耶禾特准備拒絕任何他們不想要完成的轉會，<span style=\"color: red;\">他希望把球隊建造成一股舉足輕重的力量</span>，羅渣士也獲得了保證，李斯特城不會是一家靠賣球員盈利的俱樂部。<br />\n<br />\n厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40cde3fec8b93b4bd32b9ca2bdbb0fff2b1548e","tid":1085194,"uid":103230,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"李城自己咪big6"},{"pid":"c4ef061f90c21c05463a40e329580286e0b45a4b","tid":1085194,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"d40cde3fec8b93b4bd32b9ca2bdbb0fff2b1548e","tid":1085194,"uid":103230,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"李城自己咪big6"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"雙鏝 曼城 利物浦 阿仙奴 車路士先係"},{"pid":"6792558163ae2e740831ede72b462389386facd3","tid":1085194,"uid":73340,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"c4ef061f90c21c05463a40e329580286e0b45a4b","tid":1085194,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"d40cde3fec8b93b4bd32b9ca2bdbb0fff2b1548e","tid":1085194,"uid":103230,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"李城自己咪big6"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"雙鏝 曼城 